Spark Installation guide
https://phoenixnap.com/kb/install-spark-on-windows-10

1. Download Spark from https://spark.apache.org/downloads.html
2. Download JRE
3. Download Python
4. Add SPARK, HADOOP, JAVA environment variable and path 

Pycharm Integration Guide
https://gongster.medium.com/how-to-use-pyspark-in-pycharm-ide-2fd8997b1cdd

1. Add SPARK, HADOOP, JAVA environment variable in pycharm environment variable 
2. Add content root in project structure of spark
